ndoordogpark.org/parks/cornelius-road-park\",\"name\":\"Cornelius Road Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/cornelius-road-park\",\"description\":\"Cornelius Road Park has become the premier destination for Mooresville dog owners. This facility features spacious exercise zones, experienced and certified staff, offering pet care. Their services...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Mooresville\",\"addressRegion\":\"NC\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"image\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/cornelius-road-park/cornelius-road-park-1.jpg\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dogs allowed at Lake Norman State Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, dogs are welcome on all hiking trails, such as the Lake Shore Trail, as long as they are on a leash no longer than six feet.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Does Mooresville have a dog park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"The Cornelius Road Park and nearby Stumpy Creek Park offer great walking areas, but for dedicated off-leash zones, many residents head to the Weddington Road Bark Park in nearby Concord.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the leash laws in Mooresville?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Mooresville requires dogs to be under \\\"direct control or restraint\\\" in public. This effectively means a leash is required unless in a designated off-leash area.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can dogs swim in Lake Norman?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Swimming is generally restricted at designated swim beaches, but dogs often splash in quieter coves along trails. Always check for algae blooms before letting them in the water.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Mooresville\"}]}</script><header class=\"header header-visible  header-light\"><div class=\"header-container\"><div class=\"header-left\"><a class=\"logo\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Indoor Dog Park logo\" width=\"140\" height=\"40\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;object-fit:contain;height:auto\" src=\"/images/logo/logo.png\"/></a></div><div class=\"header-center\"><nav class=\"header-nav\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/\">Browse Parks</a><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Discover <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/parks-with-bars\">Parks with Bars</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/training-facilities\">Training Facilities</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/how-it-works\">How It Works</a></div></div><div class=\"header-nav-item\"><button class=\"header-nav-link\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Locations <i class=\"bi bi-chevron-down dropdown-icon \"></i></button><div class=\"header-dropdown \"><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-francisco\">San Francisco</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/los-angeles\">Los Angeles</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/san-diego\">San Diego</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/new-york\">New York</a><a class=\"header-dropdown-link\" href=\"/cities/seattle\">Seattle</a></div></div><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"header-nav-link\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"head